        <div id="fullWidthCol">
          <h1>Deposited data search</h1>
          <p>This search allows you to discover data that has been ingested by the <a target="_blank"
              href="http://www.bgs.ac.uk/services/NGDC/home.html">National Geoscience Data Centre</a> (NGDC) and the <a
              href="http://www.bgs.ac.uk/data/NGR/home.html">National Geological Repository</a> (NGR). Use of the data
            is subject to <a href="http://www.bgs.ac.uk/services/ngdc/documents/NGDCTermsAndConditions.pdf">NGDC
              Terms and Conditions</a>. You can also find the data using the Deposited Data layers on the <a
              target="_blank" href="http://mapapps2.bgs.ac.uk/geoindex/home.html?topic=Deposited%20Data">Geoindex</a>.
          </p>
          <p>To deposit data with the NGDC please visit our <a target="_blank"
              href="http://transfer.bgs.ac.uk/ingestion">Deposit Portal</a>.</p>
          <div class="panel-top">
            <div class="panel-left">
              <form id="form" action="index.html" method="get" class="searchForm">
                <input type="hidden" name="size" value="10" />
                <ul data-tabs id="tabsMenu" class="tabsMenu">
                </ul>
                <div data-tabs-content id="tabsContent" class="tabsContent"> </div>
                <input id="search" type="button" value="Search">
                <input id="clearAllTabs" type="reset" value="Clear All Tabs">
              </form>
            </div>
            <div class="splitter"></div>
            <div class="mapContainer panel-right">
              <h3>Filter results by location</h3>
              <p class="caveat">Some results do not contain spatial data and so will not appear on the map. <br>
                Remember to clear any limitations on map before starting new search.</p>
              <div id="map" class="resultsMap"></div>
              <div class="mapFilter">
                <label for="limitExtentCheck">Limit your results to the visible map area</label>
                <input type="checkbox" id="limitExtentCheck">
                <br />
                <label for="limitRectCheck">Draw an area onto the map to limit your results to</label>
                <input type="checkbox" id="limitRectCheck">
                <button id="limitExtentRectDraw">Draw Area</button>
                <button id="limitExtentRectClear">Clear Area</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="standaloneSearchBtn">
            <button id="standaloneSearch">Search</button>
            <button id="standaloneClear">Clear Results</button>
          </div>
          <div class="splitter-horizontal"></div>
          <div id="Btns" class="panel-bottom">
            <h3>Search results <span class="resultCount__text">(<span class="resultCount__value"></span> records
                found)</span></h3>
            <span id="resultsPlaceholder">Results will be displayed here</span>
            <table id="results" class="resultsTable" style="width: 100%;">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th id="id">ID</th>
                  <th id="title">Title</th>
                  <th>Description</th>
                  <th>Actions</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="modal--background" id="modalForDetails">
            <div class="modal">
              <div class="modal--title"> Details <span aria-hidden="true" class="modal--close">&times;</span> </div>
              <div class="modal--table"> </div>
              <div class="modal--download">Download: <a class="downloadLink" target="_blank"></a></div>
              <div class="downloadTable">
                <div class="downloadTable--mainPath"> </div>
                <div class="downloadTable--files"> </div>
              </div>
              <div class="modal--metadata"> <a href="" class="modal--metadata--link" target="_blank">Go to Discovery
                  Metadata</a> </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
